      • HIDDEN_PREFIX

        static final String HIDDEN_PREFIX

        attributes starting with this prefix are considered as hidden and must not be processed (neither removed nor modified) by data mappers.

      • ANNOTATION_PREFIX

        static final String ANNOTATION_PREFIX
        Attributes starting with an '@' character are regarded as annotations, i.e. referring to data transformation parameters (normalization,...)
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • PREDICTION_PREFIX

        static final String PREDICTION_PREFIX
